headline: 3 Reasons DELL is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: What a time it’s been for Dell. In the past six months alone, the company’s stock price has increased by a massive 77%, setting a new 52-week high of $165.99 per share. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
